  "body": "We should add a `resetConnection` method to the mobile network controller for \"resetting\" the network connection. This is useful for development, for cases where you have reset a local endpoint (e.g. after restarting `ganache`).\r\n\r\nThis is part of [a larger effort to normalize the API of both network controllers](https://github.com/MetaMask/controllers/issues/971), to make them easier to merge.\r\n\r\n### Definition of Done\r\n- Whenever applies, any change unit tested, reviewed(approved) and documented(JSDOC at least)\r\n- [ ] We have changelog entries for any related changes\r\n- [ ] Any changed APIs have comprehensive inline documentation\r\n- [ ] Any changed public APIs are well covered by unit tests\r\n- Other items\r\n- [ ] If a planning/research ticket, then the plan has been reviewed and approved by at least 1 team members",
